@@TJvId3v1
Description:
This component is for reading/writing id3v1.0 tag in MP3 files. ID3 is a small tag (128 bytes for id3v1) at the end of the file who contains some informations for the song (artist, SongNameid_55>MAIN, album, comments, ...). This tag has a news version (2.0) but is not supported yet by mostly all mp3 players. You can find all inforations you want at http://www.id3.org, the official page for the id3 standard. 

